description:
Imagine being a Christian for years  faithfully attending church, hearing sermons every week, paying tithe  yet hearing Jesus say on the day of judgment, I never knew you? Unthinkable! Yet Jesus taught thats what will happen for many, even those whove spent their lives thinking theyre doing Him service. Why?

Authentic Christianity is not just finding Jesus but knowing Jesus, living with Christ, and growing in a relationship with Him until youre one with Him. So, how do you do it? What method does God use to make you like Him? What is your part in the process? Pastor Pavel Goia shares lessons from the Bible and real-life stories to illustrate how to know Jesus personally. Discover what knowing Jesus is all about!
